   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Before you start the setup, you must have a Adobe Sign account. Then, create an API
         application and configure OAuth for that application in your Adobe Sign account. After
         creating an API application, you get auth server, client ID, client secret, and redirect
         URL parameter values. These parameter values are required to create the configuration for
         Adobe Sign.</p>
